headline: Target Expands Wellness Offerings And Refocuses Stores Investors Weigh Impact
summary: Target (NYSE:TGT) is rolling out wellness brand Moon Juice and inclusive haircare label being across hundreds of stores nationwide. These moves expand Target's health and beauty assortment while aiming to strengthen the guest experience in physical stores.
